data.description: If you have been looking for a good size home with a little bit of land this gem may be the one for you. This home is tucked away behind lush greenery, offering privacy & it is sitting on 1.59 acres so you have some space too spread out a bit. The home has a huge living area, good size kitchen, large bedrooms, good size bathrooms, a oversized 2 car garage & a bonus room that could be a formal dining room, office, etc... Call your favorite agent today to schedule an appointment to see this gem.
